---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Vestara — Your Confident Exit from Landlord Life"
  description="Learn how retiring landlords use DST 1031 exchanges to sell appreciated real estate, defer capital gains tax, and earn passive income — without the headaches."
>

  <!-- =====================================================================
       HERO
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[88vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Layered gradient background -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 60%, oklch(0.65 0.18 70 / 0.12), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 15%, oklch(0.31 0.10 243 / 0.18), transparent 50%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, oklch(0.20 0.020 243) 0%, oklch(0.25 0.09 243) 55%, oklch(0.31 0.10 243) 100%);"
    ></div>

    <!-- Decorative gold rule — top left -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-56 h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #C9922A, transparent);"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-400 animate-slide-up mb-5"
           style="color: #C9922A;">
          <span class="block w-8 h-px" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
          DST 1031 Exchange Education
        </p>

        <!-- H1 -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight font-display leading-[1.08] animate-slide-up delay-100"
            style="color: oklch(0.985 0.006 80);">
          Stop Managing Properties.<br/>
          <em class="not-italic" style="color: #C9922A;">Start Enjoying</em> Retirement.
        </h1>

        <!-- Sub-headline -->
        <p class="mt-7 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-200 max-w-2xl"
           style="color: oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.85);">
          Learn how retiring landlords use DST 1031 exchanges to sell appreciated real estate,
          defer capital gains tax, and earn passive income — without the headaches.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-4 animate-slide-up delay-300">
          <a
            href="#guide"
            class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base transition-colors duration-150"
            style="background:#C9922A; color:#fff;"
            onmouseover="this.style.background='oklch(0.55 0.17 68)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.background='#C9922A'"
          >
            Get My Free DST Starter Guide
          </a>
          <a
            href="#how-it-works"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-medium transition-colors duration-150"
            style="color: oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.75);"
          >
            See how it works
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Micro-proof -->
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm animate-slide-up delay-400" style="color: oklch(0.85 0.012 76 / 0.45);">
          Free educational resource. No broker pressure. No sales calls.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative bottom fade -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-24"
         style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, oklch(0.985 0.006 80));"></div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       SOCIAL PROOF BAR
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section style="background: oklch(0.965 0.010 78); border-top: 1px solid oklch(0.92 0.012 76); border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="animate-slide-up">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">$5.4B+</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">DST equity raised annually in the U.S.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up delay-100">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">30%+</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">Capital gains tax avoided on average exchange</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up delay-200">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">4–6%</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">Typical DST annual passive income yield</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up delay-300">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">1031</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">IRS-approved exchange strategy since 2004</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-center text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.40);">
        All figures are industry educational estimates. Vestara is an educational resource, not a licensed broker or investment adviser.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       PAIN / EMPATHY SECTION
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28" style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="block w-12 h-0.5 mx-auto mb-6" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display animate-slide-up"
            style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
          You've built real wealth in real estate.<br/>
          <em class="not-italic" style="color: #C9922A;">You shouldn't have to keep earning it.</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
          The 2 a.m. tenant calls. The surprise roof replacements. The property manager who stops returning emails.
          You bought rental properties to build a retirement — not to work one.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-200"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
          But selling feels impossible. After decades of appreciation, the capital gains tax bill can wipe out
          a third of your gains — before you ever see a dollar.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold animate-slide-up delay-300"
           style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
          There is another path. It's called a DST 1031 exchange. And Vestara explains it in plain English.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       FEATURES GRID
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section id="guide" class="py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32" style="background: oklch(0.965 0.010 78);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Section header -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="block w-12 h-0.5 mx-auto mb-6" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display animate-slide-up"
            style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
          Everything you need to make a confident decision
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">
          Vestara translates complex tax law into clear, retirement-specific guidance — so you can walk
          into your CPA's office knowing exactly what to ask.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Cards grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 border animate-slide-up"
             style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
               style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            DST Explained in Plain English
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            No legal jargon, no broker spin. Our guides walk you through exactly what a Delaware Statutory
            Trust is, who qualifies, and what the IRS requires — step by step.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 border animate-slide-up delay-100"
             style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
               style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Capital Gains Tax Deferral Strategies
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Understand how a properly structured 1031 exchange lets you defer — not just reduce — the
            capital gains tax on $200K to $2M+ in embedded gains from appreciated rental properties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 border animate-slide-up delay-200"
             style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
               style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Passive Income Without Landlord Duties
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            DSTs typically distribute 4–6% annually with zero property management responsibilities.
            Learn which property types and DST structures are commonly used for retirement income goals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 border animate-slide-up delay-300"
             style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
               style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Accredited Investor Qualification Guide
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            DST investments require accredited investor status. We explain exactly what that means,
            how to confirm your eligibility, and what documentation your financial team will need.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 5 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 border animate-slide-up delay-400"
             style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
               style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Questions to Ask Your CPA or Adviser
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            We don't replace your CPA — we prepare you for the conversation. Get a printable list of the
            right questions so your professional adviser can give you the most useful guidance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 6 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 border animate-slide-up delay-500"
             style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
               style="background: oklch(0.93 0.04 240);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor" style="color: oklch(0.31 0.10 243);">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Real Numbers, Real Scenarios
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Side-by-side comparisons show what a typical landlord keeps after taxes when they sell outright
            versus completing a DST 1031 exchange — using realistic property values and gain amounts.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       HOW IT WORKS
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32" style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="block w-12 h-0.5 mx-auto mb-6" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display animate-slide-up"
            style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
          From exhausted landlord to confident retiree — in three steps
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">
          Vestara guides you through the exact knowledge you need, in the right order, so nothing gets missed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 lg:gap-16">

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start animate-slide-up">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full text-xl font-bold font-display mb-6"
               style="background: oklch(0.31 0.10 243); color: #C9922A; flex-shrink:0;">
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Understand the basics
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Read our plain-English primers on DST 1031 exchanges, capital gains tax deferral,
            and what "like-kind property" actually means in the IRS's eyes. No prior knowledge needed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start animate-slide-up delay-200">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full text-xl font-bold font-display mb-6"
               style="background: oklch(0.31 0.10 243); color: #C9922A; flex-shrink:0;">
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Run your numbers
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Use our free worksheet to estimate your embedded gains, likely tax exposure, and what passive
            income a DST exchange might realistically produce for your situation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start animate-slide-up delay-400">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full text-xl font-bold font-display mb-6"
               style="background: oklch(0.31 0.10 243); color: #C9922A; flex-shrink:0;">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display mb-3" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Talk to your team, informed
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Bring Vestara's CPA question checklist to your adviser. Walk in knowing the right questions —
            so the conversation focuses on your specific situation, not explaining the basics.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- =====================================================================
       TRUST / DIFFERENTIATOR SECTION
       ===================================================================== -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28" style="background: oklch(0.965 0.010 78);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">

        <!-- Left text -->
        <div>
          <span class="block w-12 h-0.5 mb-6" style="background:#C9922A;"></span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight font-display mb-6 animate-slide-up"
              style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">
            Education, not a sales pitch.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5 animate-slide-up delay-100"
             style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Vestara is an independent educational resource. We are not a broker-dealer, we don't sell DST
            securities, and we don't earn commissions. Our only interest is your confidence.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 animate-slide-up delay-200"
             style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.70);">
            Most information about DSTs comes from brokers who benefit from the transaction. Vestara
            was built specifically for the retiring landlord who reads Kiplinger and trusts their CPA —
            and wants to understand the strategy <em>before</em> anyone tries to sell them something.
          </p>
          <a href="#cta"
             class="inline-block px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base transition-colors duration-150 animate-slide-up delay-300"
             style="background: oklch(0.31 0.10 243); color: #fff;">
            Read the free guide
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Right stat callouts -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 p-6 rounded-2xl border animate-slide-up delay-100"
               style="background: oklch(0.985 0.006 80); border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                 style="background: oklch(0.65 0.18 70 / 0.15);">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="#C9922A">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-base" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">No commissions, ever</p>
              <p class="text-sm mt-1 leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.65);">
                Vestara earns nothing if you complete an exchange. Our guidance is independent by design.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5 p-6 rounded-2xl border animate-slide-up delay-200"
